{"tid":2493439,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"另類中學｜校內飼養20多隻巨龜　蠎蛇及泰加巨蜥　學生為照顧爬蟲愛上返學：被蛇纏身很舒服","createTime":"2021-04-18T02:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T23:44:22.000Z","uid":271829,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"81b8f52edfa52ef06fd298c8b23653367c0fafff","tid":2493439,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8rQuGxzwU3DQ-WIS53YOelN5Gdg=/802x474/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C3ZSPISB5FC6TFEIMHH7D2SJAY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8rQuGxzwU3DQ-WIS53YOelN5Gdg%3D%2F802x474%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC3ZSPISB5FC6TFEIMHH7D2SJAY.JPG&h=04047303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n慕光英文書院「亞馬遜生物教室」由不同年級的同學共同打理：（後排左起）中一張珈熒、中二萬崇婧、中二曾雅婷、中二鄧文諾、中二陳業誠、中四王家謙；（前排左起） 中二楊梓穎、中四萬恩彤、中二周子楠、中一謝海澄、中四梁銘軒。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n泰加巨蜥、球蟒、盾臂龜、豹紋陸龜、鬃獅蜥、南美角蛙、變色龍、石龍子、守宮...... 一般人可能畢生都沒有機會一次過飼養以上所有動物。而在香港，就有一班中學生很幸福，學校裏飼養了廿多隻珍禽異獸，每日都「攞正牌」跟這班爬蟲動物零距離生活。<br />\n<br />\n慕光英文書院「亞馬遜生物教室」<br />\n位於觀塘的直資學校慕光英文書院發展STEM課程，斥資200萬元興建了「亞馬遜生物教室」，上年度正式啟用。學校從漁農自然護理署、香港兩棲及爬蟲協會等不同機構收養各種爬蟲動物，養在生物教室內悉心照顧。購買食材、餵食、清理糞便、放風散步、更換籠內底材等日常照顧，主力由一班兩棲及爬蟲學會的同學們分工負責。<br />\n爬蟲動物總是被人誤解，有毒、兇猛、會咬人、醜陋......把蛇或泰加放出來爬行，少不免引來一陣雞飛狗走。但兩爬學會的同學將牠們視若珍寶，每個小息或放學後都自願跑到生物教室幫手，把蛇、鬃獅蜥抱上身也毫不畏懼。不怕髒不怕臭不怕累，同學們說生物教室是實現他們願望的地方，是他們的驕傲。為了動物的健康，他們會自己去翻書學習、上網查找資料，蛇怎樣探測熱能、龜為甚麼不能吃太高草酸、爬蟲動物怎樣分性別，相關知識他們娓娓道來。他們給了爬蟲動物一個家，爬蟲動物讓他們發展出堅持、責任心、自行學習的能力。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210418/BZTNYQZFIRCLVDWSRUXMQP4MUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210418%2FBZTNYQZFIRCLVDWSRUXMQP4MUM%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RBOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=6d466b74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210418%2FBZTNYQZFIRCLVDWSRUXMQP4MUM%2F&h=ead00f17\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210418/BZTNYQZFIRCLVDWSRUXMQP4MUM/</a>"},{"pid":"9b41f1daa9935f489faa7b951858b899669f3dd0","tid":2493439,"uid":161159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abeeef945a9c891c1c83c19450fbe45be4ed2e93","tid":2493439,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887edde853b7c5b999807e5477dd8d561cd65d37","tid":2493439,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:19:09.000Z","msg":"其實由細到大去接觸依啲嘢真係唔會驚。好似由細到大俾十萬隻甲由包圍都會變得唔驚甲由"},{"pid":"cde2fa28693624ac1e9c7a8b693565547790fc7a","tid":2493439,"uid":240682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:43:19.000Z","msg":"搞到我都想番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e194964c7127c9161a46ea5299259ea0af51031","tid":2493439,"uid":59684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都想讀"},{"pid":"b1479d855e6edfb394b4852d936bc76219294ef5","tid":2493439,"uid":48080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"887edde853b7c5b999807e5477dd8d561cd65d37","tid":2493439,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T02:19:09.000Z","msg":"其實由細到大去接觸依啲嘢真係唔會驚。好似由細到大俾十萬隻甲由包圍都會變得唔驚甲由"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T17:17:17.000Z","msg":"細細個比十幾萬隻甲由圍應該會有童年陰影<img src=\"/a